ce3fb4ea-fcb4-41a9-ab18-a42910fd8306.a5a8b7f1-542e-43e8-922b-3d82347f96c5.description=list cleared from global context ce3fb4ea-fcb4-41a9-ab18-a42910fd8306.ad073b08-4442-47e4-b3a2-e25c81299530.description=Adds the newest value to the list of values. ce3fb4ea-fcb4-41a9-ab18-a42910fd8306.c87dbc76-0a1e-4ea3-b577-90106c4ed4eb.description=checks how much time has elapsed, determining whether or not the averager should continue to loop. ce3fb4ea-fcb4-41a9-ab18-a42910fd8306.d5e4ff43-604c-4808-9459-05f51cf07ccb.transition.description=Value added to list. ce3fb4ea-fcb4-41a9-ab18-a42910fd8306.description=Loops over a specified amount of time and averages a value fed into it over this time. Checks to see if this value is above or below a specified threshold. This flow should only be used as a subflow since using it on its own will always return the continue response unless runLength is assigned a value of 0. When this flow gives the continue response the calling flow must obtain another value, and pass it to this flow again. inputs\: runLength - the number of seconds this flow should loop. waitTime - the number of seconds this flow should before returning when looping. threshold - A value to compare the averaged value to. VALUE - the value of the most recent function call, which will be added to the average. keyName - the key that the list of values will be stored in until averaging. responses\: less than - The average was less than the threshold. equal - the average was the same as the threshold. greater than - the average was greater than the threshold. Continue - the specified amount of time has not yet passed, the calling flow should run another operation and pass this flow another value. failure - values in keyName could not be averaged. additional results\: average - the average value of the list. only a result is the response is success. List - a list that is accumulating values. This is erased when the time runs out. timeStarted - the time since you made the first function call. this is erased when time runs out. ce3fb4ea-fcb4-41a9-ab18-a42910fd8306.ee4b0f8e-d03a-4eba-8fa5-207a1b7dc98d.transition.description=List saved to global context ce3fb4ea-fcb4-41a9-ab18-a42910fd8306.fbb59dd7-73aa-4814-933b-9bbc4a5134d2.transition.description=List cleared from global context.
